title: No. 5 Utah uses 6 takeaways to beat No. 23 California 30-24 (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,191 No. 5 Utah uses 6 takeaways to beat No. 23 California 30-24 (Yahoo Sports) The Utes sent a message Saturday night that they have no plans on going anywhere but up. Utah had a season-high six takeaways, picking off five of Jared Goff's passes. Cal had one last possession and drove to the 21, but Boobie Hobbs knocked down Goff's fourth-down pass with 26 seconds left.
